iv></div></div></section></div></div><div class="_annotation_vyjtl_78 _content_1t3mx_1 contentAnnotation" data-component="annotation" data-testid="annotation_testID" id="content"><p><span>Tipplers, discover the delights of 10 of the latest additions to Bangkok’s buzzing nightlife milieu – from throbbing dancefloors to cocktails close to the heavens. Add them to your </span><a href="https://www.timeout.com/bangkok/things-to-do/best-things-to-do-in-bangkok"><span> </span><span>best things to do in the metropolis list</span></a><span>. </span><span>Just sip smart, drink responsibly and let the good times flow.</span></p></div></div><div data-component="interscroller"></div><div class="zone _zoneFirst_367pt_5 _zone_367pt_1 _container_1t43t_1" data-component="lazy-load-zone" data-params=''{"zoneId":"84790986","url":"/595/en-US/pages/167048/zone/84790986?site_id=th-bangkok&amp;pageNumber=:pageNumber&amp;pageSize=50&amp;gp-web=true"}'' data-testid="zone-large-list_testID" data-zone-name="large_list"><div class="_zoneItems_1t43t_5 zoneItems"><article class="tile _article_osmln_1" data-testid="tile-zone-large-list_testID"><div class="articleContent _articleContent_osmln_229"><div class="_title_osmln_9"><a class="" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"category":"GP Engagement","label":"in content","action":"link - internal"}}'' data-testid="tile-link_testID" href="/bangkok/bars/apt-101" rel="" target="_self"><h3 class="_h3_c6c0h_1" data-testid="tile-title_testID">APT 101</h3></a></div><div class="_tileTags_osmln_50"><section class="_tags_1i2cm_17" data-testid="tags_testID"><ul class="_tagsList_1i2cm_17"><li class="_tag_1i2cm_17"><span class="_text_1i2cm_68">Asok</span></li></ul></section></div><div class="_imageContainer_osmln_46"><a class="tileImageLink" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"category":"GP Engagement","label":"in content","action":"link - internal"}}'' data-testid="tile-link_testID" href="/bangkok/bars/apt-101" rel="" target="_self"><div class="_imageWrap_osmln_94 _imageWrapDesktop_osmln_98"><picture><source height="422" srcset="https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/400/225/image.webp 400w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/750/422/image.webp 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1024/576/image.webp 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1372/772/image.webp 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1536/864/image.webp 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1920/1080/image.webp 1920w" type="image/webp" width="750"/><img alt="APT 101" class="_image_osmln_46 aspect-ratio-16-9" data-testid="responsive-image_testID" height="422" loading="lazy" sizes="auto" src="https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/750/422/image.jpg" srcset="https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/400/225/image.jpg 400w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/750/422/image.jpg 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1024/576/image.jpg 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1372/772/image.jpg 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1536/864/image.jpg 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1920/1080/image.jpg 1920w" title="APT 101" width="750"/></picture></div><div class="_imageWrap_osmln_94 _imageWrapMobile_osmln_208"><picture><source height="562" srcset="https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/380/285/image.webp 380w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/750/562/image.webp 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1024/768/image.webp 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1372/1029/image.webp 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1536/1152/image.webp 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1920/1440/image.webp 1920w" type="image/webp" width="750"/><img alt="APT 101" class="_image_osmln_46 aspect-ratio-4-3" data-testid="responsive-image_testID" height="562" loading="lazy" sizes="auto" src="https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/750/562/image.jpg" srcset="https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/380/285/image.jpg 380w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/750/562/image.jpg 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1024/768/image.jpg 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1372/1029/image.jpg 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1536/1152/image.jpg 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1920/1440/image.jpg 1920w" title="APT 101" width="750"/></picture></div><figcaption class="_figcaption_18vpl_1" data-testid="image-credits_testID"><span>Photograph: APT 101</span></figcaption></a></div><div class="_summaryContainer_osmln_364"><div class="_summary_osmln_21"><div class="_p_1mmxl_1" data-testid="summary_testID"><p><strong>What''s the vibe?</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> APT 101 isn’t just a club; it’s a retro-inspired space that channels the glamour of 1970s New York with a Bangkok twist. Soft lighting, a crackling fireplace, and mid-century decor create a cosy yet stylish atmosphere perfect for unwinding. Inspired by RH, a legendary New York designer, the space is hosted by a mysterious figure who adds a layer of intrigue. Start your evening at the Pantry with sundowners from 6pm, a relaxed spot for after-work drinks and small plates, with live music setting the tone every Friday. Come May, the Arcade opens – a nostalgic room filled with vintage games and vinyl spinning all night. End your night at the Clubhouse, APT 101’s main stage, where disco house, afro house, and melodic beats keep the energy alive until late.</span></p>\n<p><strong>What to drink:</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Give crimson velvet (B400) a go – a deep, reddish-brown beauty that’s as bold, smooth and effortlessly stylish as a night spent grooving under the glittering lights.</span></p>\n<p><strong>When to visit: </strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> When you fancy a trip to 1970s New York, but make it Bangkok.</span></p>\n<p><strong>APT 101, 3rd Floor, 233 Sukhumvit Rd (Corner of Soi 17), Khwaeng Khlong Toei Nuea, Watthana, Bangkok 10110. 02-821-5813. Open daily 6pm onwards</strong></p>\n<p><br/><br/><br/></p></div></div></div><div class="_ctaButtons_osmln_107"><div class="_cta_osmln_107 _viewMoreCta_osmln_128"><a class="_secondary_1gagn_22" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"action":"link - internal","category":"GP Engagement","label":"read more button"}}'' data-testid="view-more-cta_testID" href="/bangkok/bars/apt-101" rel="" target="_self"><span class="_textContent_1gagn_69">Read more</span></a></div></div></div></article><article class="tile _article_osmln_1" data-testid="tile-zone-large-list_testID"><div class="articleContent _articleContent_osmln_229"><div class="_title_osmln_9"><a class="" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"category":"GP Engagement","label":"in content","action":"link - internal"}}'' data-testid="tile-link_testID" href="/bangkok/bars/rubys" rel="" target="_self"><h3 class="_h3_c6c0h_1" data-testid="tile-title_testID">Ruby''s</h3></a></div><div class="_tileTags_osmln_50"><section class="_tags_1i2cm_17" data-testid="tags_testID"><ul class="_tagsList_1i2cm_17"><li class="_tag_1i2cm_17"><span class="_text_1i2cm_68">Phloen Chit</span></li></ul></section></div><div class="_imageContainer_osmln_46"><a class="tileImageLink" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"category":"GP Engagement","label":"in content","action":"link - internal"}}'' data-testid="tile-link_testID" href="/bangkok/bars/rubys" rel="" target="_self"><div class="_imageWrap_osmln_94 _imageWrapDesktop_osmln_98"><picture><source height="422" srcset="https://media.timeout.com/images/106205565/400/225/image.webp 400w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106205565/750/422/image.webp 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106205565/1024/576/image.webp 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106205565/1372/772/image.webp 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106205565/1536/864/image.webp 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106205565/1920/1080/image.webp 1920w" type="image/webp" width="750"/>