INSERT INTO places VALUES(312,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/article/bangkoks-best-rooftop-bars#Finalist:_Com’On_Bar','<article>Finalist: Com’On Bar</article>','2025-09-06 11:35:17.699887',13.739951999999999721,100.51782099999999608,'114 Trok Salak Hin, Khwaeng Rong Muang, Pathum Wan, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10330, Thailand','ChIJJyFLaCSZ4jAR0XH5sj7ScQw','https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJJyFLaCSZ4jAR0XH5sj7ScQw','Finalist: Com’On Bar','Bar','One of the youngest entries to crack this list in years, opening in just 2023, Com’On Bar’s location just on the outskirts of the city’s old town keeps it far away from the gleaming high rises of the business districts, allowing its perch on the seventh floor to offer 270-degree views of the surrounding area, which the bar team gives nods too through their area-themed drinks like the smoky-flavored “Old Town” the housing number of the building with the crisp “One One Four”. A respectable selection of craft beers on tap rounds out the menu.','Perched on the seventh floor, this bar offers stunning 270-degree views of the city. The menu features area-themed cocktails like the smoky ''Old Town'' and a solid selection of craft beers on tap. A laid-back vibe makes it perfect for enjoying drinks while soaking in the scenery.','bar,craft beer,city views',NULL,'{"Fri": ["17:30-24:00"], "Sat": ["00:00-01:00", "17:30-24:00"], "Sun": ["00:00-01:00"]}','summarized',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-08 05:59:22.365930',NULL,'OPERATIONAL',420,'gpt',3);
INSERT INTO places VALUES(313,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/article/bangkoks-best-rooftop-bars#ThreeSixty_Rooftop_Bar','<article>ThreeSixty Rooftop Bar</article>','2025-09-06 11:35:17.702832',13.728800199999999787,100.51131330000000474,'123 Charoen Nakhon Rd, Khwaeng Khlong Ton Sai, Khet Khlong San, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10600, Thailand','ChIJbSLDx92Y4jARM9xY2YMxPN8','https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJbSLDx92Y4jARM9xY2YMxPN8','ThreeSixty Rooftop Bar','Rooftop','Head up to Bangkok’s sky-high Peruvian-Japanese rooftop restaurant and bar in Bangkok for panoramic sunset views, zesty pisco sours, and innovative fusion cocktails. They provide Nikkei food, a combination of Peruvian and Japanese cuisine, so be sure to try the ceviche sampling plate, tacos, or the South American grilled platter. The rooftop''s sleek and fashionable design draws inspiration from Central Park in New York City, and the space is outfitted with artificial grass, wooden structure trees, neon blue and pink lights, a maze, and, to top it all off, a bathroom with a view of the Bangkok cityscape.','A stylish rooftop bar offers stunning sunset views over Bangkok while serving creative Peruvian-Japanese fusion cocktails and dishes. Signature drinks include zesty pisco sours, complemented by a ceviche sampling plate and grilled platters. The space features artificial grass and vibrant neon lights, adding to its chic ambiance.','rooftop,bar,fusion cuisine,cocktails',NULL,'{"Mon": ["00:00-01:00", "17:00-24:00"], "Tue": ["00:00-01:00", "17:00-24:00"], "Wed": ["00:00-01:00", "17:00-24:00"], "Thu": ["00:00-01:00", "17:00-24:00"], "Fri": ["00:00-01:00", "17:00-24:00"], "Sat": ["00:00-01:00", "17:00-24:00"], "Sun": ["17:00-24:00", "00:00-01:00"]}','summarized',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-07 08:43:07',NULL,'OPERATIONAL',420,'gpt',2);
