INSERT INTO places VALUES(483,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/news/30-bangkok-nightlife-spots-opened-2024-you-to-check-out#6','<article>Frog Bar</article>','2025-09-08 04:04:14.301174',13.738854000000000343,100.57638070000001206,'237 Sukhumvit 49, Khwaeng Khlong Tan Nuea, Watthana, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10110, Thailand','ChIJkXOkMQCf4jAReYwX-bUHq-Q','https://maps.google.com/?cid=ChIJkXOkMQCf4jAReYwX-bUHq-Q','Frog Bar','Bar','Filled with Japanese literary and pop culture references familiar to Thai customers, the drinks take cues from Japanese beats and blend it with local ingredients. The first welcome shot is a Nikolaschka which appeared in the 2024 anime of the popular “Bartender” manga. The main portion of the drink, however, steals a couple of pages from Haruki Murakami’s award winning “Hard-Boiled Wonderland and the End of the World”, splitting the cocktail menu into classics with a twist and new creations.','A vibrant bar infused with Japanese literary and pop culture, offering unique cocktails that blend local ingredients. Specialties include a welcome shot inspired by the ''Bartender'' manga and a menu featuring classic drinks with creative twists. Perfect for those seeking a cultural drink experience in a lively atmosphere.','cocktails,Japanese culture,bar',NULL,'{"openNow": false, "periods": [{"open": {"day": 2, "hour": 19, "minute": 0}, "close": {"day": 3, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 3, "hour": 19, "minute": 0}, "close": {"day": 4, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 4, "hour": 19, "minute": 0}, "close": {"day": 5, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 5, "hour": 19, "minute": 0}, "close": {"day": 6, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 6, "hour": 19, "minute": 0}, "close": {"day": 0, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}], "weekdayDescriptions": ["Monday: Closed", "Tuesday: 7:00\u202fPM\u2009\u2013\u200912:00\u202fAM", "Wednesday: 7:00\u202fPM\u2009\u2013\u200912:00\u202fAM", "Thursday: 7:00\u202fPM\u2009\u2013\u200