INSERT INTO places VALUES(528,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/restaurants/news/50-new-bangkok-restaurants-opened-2024-you-to-check-out#15','<article>Fatboy Izakaya Amarin</article>','2025-09-08 04:22:21.334075',13.743908299999998412,100.54120140000000205,'Gaysorn Amarin ชั้น 3 496 Thanon Phloen Chit, Khwaeng Lumphini, Pathum Wan, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10330, Thailand','ChIJS4Om4KSf4jAR14xLUQtLkLg','https://maps.google.com/?cid=ChIJS4Om4KSf4jAR14xLUQtLkLg','Fatboy Izakaya Amarin','Restaurant','The city’s favorite space for Japanese food with a party vibe, Fatboy Izakaya, has finally opened another branch at the newly renovated Gaysorn Amarin, serving everyone’s grub and drinks—now with a view. Currently, they share the same menu with the Ekkamai branch but some exclusive Gaysorn additions are in the making. The crowd pleasing side snack, a bowl of crispy chicken skin (B140) is similar to pork scratching (kap moo) and maintains its crunchy texture for hours. And, of course, you just can’t resist ordering the signature Fatboy Roll (750). Coming in a platter of eight, the maki is stuffed with fresh cucumber, cream cheese, and a tender wagyu with an extra strip of thinly sliced foie gras on top.','A lively spot for Japanese cuisine, this izakaya offers a vibrant atmosphere complemented by a scenic view. Specialties include crispy chicken skin and the signature Fatboy Roll, featuring fresh ingredients and luxurious toppings. Perfect for social gatherings, the venue promises a fun dining experience.','Japanese,Izakaya,Casual Dining',NULL,'{"openNow": true, "periods": [{"open": {"day": 0, "hour": 11, "minute": 30}, "close": {"day": 1, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 1, "hour": 11, "minute": 30}, "close": {"day": 2, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 2, "hour": 11, "minute": 30}, "close": {"day": 3, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 3, "hour": 11, "minute": 30}, "close": {"day": 4, "hour": 0, "minute": 0}}, {"open": {"day": 4, "hour": 11,